    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/card/10_1007_s00044_016_1764_y__task_003/000",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "on average, three organisms are reported per chemical structure and eleven structures per organism. Notably, half of all structures have been reported from a single organism and half of all studied organisms are reported to contain five or fewer structures.",
      "asbval:note": "The research question is semantically equivalent to the paper's analysis of organism-structure distribution. Figure 4 explicitly shows 'Distribution of structures per organism' with binning by count ranges.",
