      "asbval:drift_notes": [
        "The card references a specific script name '5_addingOTL.R' which is not explicitly mentioned in the paper passages. The paper describes the organism enrichment workflow but does not name individual R scripts with numeric prefixes in the organism processing section.",
        "The expected output file path 'interim/dictionaries/organism/otl.sqlite' is not mentioned in the passages. While the paper discusses custom dictionaries and their archival, no specific SQLite output file at this path is documented.",
