      "asbval:evidence_quote": "The Python version used was 3.7.12 up to 3.9.7, and the Python packages utilized were, in alphabetical order:... pandas (1.3.4)... All scripts used for the generation of the figures are available in the lotus-processor repository in the src/4_visualizing directory for reproducibility.",
