      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "InChI were translated to SMILES using the RDKit, 2021 implementation in Python 3.8 (src/2_curating/2_editing/structure/1_translating/inchi.py)... The Python version used was 3.7.12 up to 3.9.7, and the Python packages utilized were, in alphabetical order: ... rdkit (2021.09.2) (RDKit, 2021)...",
      "asbval:note": "Python 3 (versions 3.7.12\u20133.9.7) is explicitly confirmed as the execution environment for chemical structure processing, including RDKit-based sanitization.",
