    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/count-verification-against-published-values/005",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Bulk retrieval of a frozen (2021-12-20) version of LOTUS data is also available at https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5794106 (Rutz et al., 2021a)... The download lotus part of lotus-wikidata-interact allows the download of all chemical compounds with a \"found in taxon\" property... It makes a copy of all the entities (compounds, taxa, references) into a local triplestore that can be queried with SPARQL as is or converted to a TSV file for inclusion in other projects.",
      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms availability of frozen TSV/CSV data files for independent analysis.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-7554-elife-70780",
