      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "To assess the validity of the obtained results, a randomized set of 420 referenced structure-organism pairs was sampled in each reference subcategory and validated or rejected manually... Based on this first manually validated dataset, filtering criteria (src/r/filter_dirty.R) were established to maximize precision and recall.",
      "asbval:note": "Paper uses manual validation sampling as a checkpoint to detect errors and validate filtering criteria against gold-standard curated entries.",
