      "asbval:evidence_quote": "A snapshot of the obtained data at the time of re-submission (2021-12-20) is available at the following Zenodo community: https://zenodo.org/communities/the-lotus-initiative... Bulk retrieval of a frozen (2021-12-20) version of LOTUS data is also available at https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5794106",
