      "asbval:target_claim_field": "research_question",
      "asbval:target_claim_text": "Systematically verify the completeness and accuracy of a curated structure-organism dataset by reproducing reported aggregate statistics (unique pairs, structures, organisms, sources) and comparing observed counts against published benchmarks using absolute and relative differenc",
