      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "A snapshot of the obtained data at the time of re-submission (2021-12-20) is available at the following Zenodo community: https://zenodo.org/communities/the-lotus-initiative and related record: 5793224 (Rutz et al., 2021e), 5794107 (Rutz et al., 2021c), 5794597 (Rutz et al., 2021b), 5801816 (Rutz, 2021)... At its current stage of development, LOTUS disseminates 750,000+ referenced structure-organism pairs.",
