      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/frequency-distribution-binning/007",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "At its current stage of development, LOTUS disseminates 750,000+ referenced structure-organism pairs... The LOTUS processing pipeline is tailored to efficiently include and diffuse novel or curated data directly from new sources or at the Wikidata level.",
      "asbval:note": "LOTUS explicitly manages structure-organism pair tables as its core data model.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-7554-elife-70780",
