      "asbval:note": "Paper mentions sanitization via MolVS package and references scripts in src/2_curating/2_editing/structure/ directory, but does not explicitly name 'sanitizing.py'. The actual sanitization is performed via MolVS (Python package), not a standalone sanitizing.py script. The paper references naming.R (R script) for sanitization details, not a Python script.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-7554-elife-70780",
